  "texts": [
    "Due to being able to process large volumes of data faster than humans, these robotic agents will play a key role in the post-scarcity digital memory ecosystem that is likely to define memory communication in the upcoming decades.",
    "Besides, robotic agents will serve as a crucial factor in shaping the relations of power and inequalities in the context of individual and collective remembrance.",
    "The current concerns about AI systems amplifying discrimination and disempowerment of vulnerable communities (e.g.",
    "Birhane 2021; Kalluri 2020) stress the importance of considering the risks associated with the impact of robotic agents on memory practices which are profoundly affected by the relations of cultural, political, and economic power.",
    "Despite the importance of communication involving robotic agents, the state of research on them in the field of memory studies currently remains limited."
  ],
